title: Medtronic Results to Provide Checkup on Covidien Deal
text:
Multibillion-dollar acquisitions can be thrilling for investors. What happens next, though less exciting, can be just as important.
Medtronic PLC on Thursday reports first-quarter results for its fiscal 2016 year ending in April. This will mark the second round of results since the device manufacturerâ€™s $50 billion acquisition of Covidien PLC...
